T1  - Development and Validation of a Fact-Checking Algorithm to Enhance the Explainability of a Retrieval-Augmented Generation-Based Large Language Model for Radio-Oncological Clinical Questions
AU  - Domres, A.
AU  - Vladika, J.
AU  - Nguyen, M.
AU  - Moser, R.
AU  - Bernhardt, D.
AU  - Combs, S.E.
AU  - Borm, K.
