T1  - Large Language Model–Supported Identification of Intellectual Disabilities in Clinical Free-Text Summaries: Mixed Methods Study
AU  - Edwards, Aleksandra
AU  - Pardiñas, Antonio F
AU  - Kirov, George
AU  - Rees, Elliott
AU  - Camacho-Collados, Jose
